Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=4}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.42,0:00:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.54,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ayane{**-chan}, c-could you repeat that one more time?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.36,0:00:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}, calm down, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} calm!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.30,0:00:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's right, Serika!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't panic!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.81,0:00:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, you're shaking.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.52,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan}, are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.37,0:00:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.42,0:00:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through all the documents we acquired,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.95,0:00:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and it definitely seems that Kaiser Loan \nhas been funding the Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.23,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's really true,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.27,0:00:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,then those jerks from the Helmet Gang,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.90,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the same people who've been trying to gun us down,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.91,0:00:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,have been buying their weapons using {\i1}our{\i0} money!
Comment: 10,0:02:17.75,0:02:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hoshino noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, there it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.67,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Collected 7.88 million.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, isn't this...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's exactly what you think it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.03,0:02:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something special \nabout this 7.88 million?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, could this be...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.10,0:02:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is the exact amount we paid them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.81,0:02:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,7.88 million is a lot. \nYou were in that much debt?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only a fraction. The total is over 900 million.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.96,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, we can get into \nthe finer details some other time.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This document lists all of Kaiser Loan's cash flows.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.45,0:02:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we see a figure that matches \nour 7.88 million payment down to the yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.99,0:03:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to have come from \nthe debt collector that visits our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's this.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after depositing the 7.88 million yen,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.51,0:03:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they allocated 5 million yen towards \n"strategic allocations" to the Kata Kata Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.58,0:03:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Strategic allocations...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.81,0:03:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They sent the Kata Kata Helmet Gang \nfive million yen to help fund their job.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Job?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.15,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably to take us out of the picture.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.52,0:03:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It means Kaiser Loan has been \nour true enemy all along!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would they do this?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If the school went bankrupt,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,they wouldn't be able to get back \nthe money they loaned us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.06,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you say Kaiser Loan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.34,0:03:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the loan sharks run by \nthe infamous Kaiser Corporation, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.61,0:04:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt Kaiser Loan is acting on its own.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.51,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Corporation's main branch \nmust be involved in this as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.32,0:04:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me earlier!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.82,0:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it. If anything, we should be \napologizing for dragging you into our mess.
Comment: 10,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahaha {hifumi_laugh.jpeg --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.91,0:04:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll report this situation to the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.22,0:04:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaiser Corporation must have ties \nto criminals and other underground dealings.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And this could help prove it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.76,0:04:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, now that I've gotten to know you, \nI can't leave you to fend for yourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.15,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If Trinity's student council could lend us a hand, \nwe'd be in a much better position.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.65,0:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, this has been quite a shock.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.53,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're a billion yen in debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not {\i1}that{\i0} much! It's only 960 mil—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.02,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}, she was just rounding it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.08,0:05:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In any case, I'm sure once \nthe Tea Party hears about this—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure it's old news to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just over at the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.93,0:05:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet the hotshots over at Gehenna \nand Millenium all know already.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.26,0:05:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? But if they know what's going on, then why?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.45,0:05:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew, and simply chose not to do anything about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They chose not to?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you mean well, and I appreciate it,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but the world's a bit more complex than that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.65,0:05:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you went ahead and told them, \nit might just complicate things for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.15,0:05:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it. Abydos is \non the verge of shutting down, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.08,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a whole lot's gonna stop these schools \nfrom asking us to "return the favour" for helping us.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm getting at?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.31,0:05:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, basically, if they said they'd help \nbut then took advantage of the situation,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you would be powerless to stop them?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.34,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}, aren't you being a bit too cynical?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.74,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We could really use all the help we can get.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's always the off chance, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The off chance...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooooh, this is a tough one.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll find a way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.50,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be {\i1}something{\i0} we can do, r-right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, c'mon!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some conviction at least!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.85,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, thinking about this logically...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then quit thinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.88,0:06:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, everyone was looking at me, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.51,0:06:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Of course everyone was gonna look at you \nif you said something at that moment.{alt style :gundako: -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}C'mon, you should be used to this by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And anyway you're—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.78,0:06:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{*}Teacher{*Sensei} is doing the best he can to help us.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The off chance, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.83,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's precisely because we neglected \nthe off chance that Abydos ended up like this.
Comment: 10,0:06:54.17,0:06:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hoshino noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.22,0:07:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, let this old soul in on the fun. \nWhat's all the chatter about?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't believe this. \nHifumi{**-san} was just saying—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.49,0:07:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying what? Mind repeating it, Faust{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.14,0:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the proud leader of the Masked Swimsuit Gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am most definitely {\i1}not{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, quit picking on Hifumi!
Comment: 10,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hifumi_laugh.jpeg --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I should get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure {\i1}you{\i0} had fun, \nbut what about the rest of us?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.59,0:07:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll drop by one of these days, \nso let's hang out then.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi, good luck out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.13,0:07:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's tough, but I'll be cheering you on!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye for now!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.66,0:07:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we'll really be okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.18,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's not dwell on it anymore for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all tuckered out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's meet back up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home and rest up for today, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.82,0:08:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.99,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.90,0:08:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3046,4088,\c&H000000&)}Staying up late is bad for your skin, y'know?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.46,0:08:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good m—Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru{**-chan}, were you up all night or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I caught a few winks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.58,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aru{**-chan}. We've come up \nwith a new plan to attack Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kayoko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We plant explosives in key locations ahead of time,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.46,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and when they get near them, \nwe blow them to kingdom come.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka's out making preparations...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I heard you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about some things.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.98,0:08:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be sure, can we go ahead with this plan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.14,0:09:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you're losing sleep over it,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.36,0:09:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we just take the money \nthey left behind and put it towards our funds?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.56,0:09:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This money is something \nthose girls left behind by accident.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Using it would just be uncool.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,True outlaws wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.54,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't we get an advance from the client?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.26,0:09:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No upfront payments. \nThat's the one policy I refuse to break.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been over this, haven't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.29,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because accepting payment in advance \nmeans we're forced to comply with their demands.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.66,0:09:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Comment: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Mesugaki noises} {who is responsible for this --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, that may ring a bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.97,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We only take money for \na job well done. No exceptions.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.68,0:09:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we waver, we'll never achieve the vision \nwe've strived for for so long.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.80,0:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Our vision? We had one?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.24,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a group of hard-boiled outlaws, \nunshackled by rules or laws!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.98,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the vision of Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.32,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, boss, we could always just \nthrow in the towel and go back to Gehenna.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.37,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't the Prefect Team \nbe all over us if we did that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.56,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. The Prefect Team would be a problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.38,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,QC,A {\i1}big{\i0} problem. They're the \nstrongest group in all of Kivotos, no?{@ML: went back and forth over "team", "group", "squad", "players", etc over this. thoughts? -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.42,0:10:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's only because of \nthe Head Prefect, Hina.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.17,0:10:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no exaggeration to say the bulk \nof their firepower comes from just her.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.27,0:10:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the rest of them should be easy pickings.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.28,0:10:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} some confidence. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, only if we play our cards right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.55,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Going back to Gehenna is not an option.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.02,0:10:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for a group of hard-boiled outlaws, \nunshackled by rules or laws.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.58,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Problem Solver 68's \nvision or whatever, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Haruka.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Had fun out there?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Comment: 10,0:11:02.23,0:11:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Aru, just give me the word.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say the word.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.69,0:11:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow it all to smithereens for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,With my own two hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, Aru{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like someone's hungry!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shut it, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna grab a bite?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.19,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we thinking? Ramen over at Shiba Seki?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.68,0:11:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the part-timer.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She only works in the afternoon, so we're good.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.47,0:11:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. Come on, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Haruka. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, coming.
Comment: 10,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{yawn.jpeg}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're early today.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.{OJISAAAAAAAAAAN} {I sense a remarkable force behind this comment --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.15,0:11:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing here this early?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.39,0:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I've got dibs on this lap.\n This is my special napping spot.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't going to join you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.51,0:12:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon now, Hoshino{**-senpai}. \nThere's enough lap for both of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really. I wasn't going to join her...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.69,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy daisy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's my day off.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.08,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go kill time somewhere else, \nso give me a holler if you need me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose she's off to take a nap?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's good weather for a nap.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.53,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}'s changed a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.33,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She acts like a lazy sleepyhead nowadays,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.86,0:12:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but back when I first met her,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.79,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,she always looked like she was \nweighed down by something.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Weighed down? By what?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.20,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything and everything, I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.57,0:12:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I heard, back when Hoshino{**-senpai} enrolled, \nthere used to be another older student here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she was the last \nstudent council president Abydos ever had.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So once she was gone,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.03,0:13:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai} ended up shouldering \nall the responsibilities alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She was only a first-year at the time, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if that was why,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's always been against involving other schools.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mellowed out a lot since then.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.93,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like I was there, \nso I only know so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.14,0:13:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because I'm here now?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why she changed.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, you know...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to say is...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks fer waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.20,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking forward to this!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.21,0:14:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,O-One bowl per person?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for us to have all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry 'bout it. \nY'all came all the way over just for my ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.97,0:14:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What more's there to say?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.54,0:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you so much! \nFrom the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We really can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll have to enjoy this gracious gift.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.75,0:14:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give ya a li'l extra on the house, \nso eat your fill, y'hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.99,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend o' Serika's a friend o' mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange how it's so empty when the food's this good.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just the location?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.55,0:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,People have been leaving \nbecause of the desertification, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not their friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're making a scene.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've figured out what my problem is.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this restaurant!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhhh, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you liked the ramen here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has good food, \ngives very generous portions,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people here are nothing but nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.56,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see? All of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here on business!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to be hard-boiled outlaws!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But this cozy atmosphere is turning us \ninto {\i1}soft{\i0}-boiled outlaws! {A+ --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.55,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be honest, you've lost me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.17,Alt,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,***,Haruka?
Comment: 10,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,***,Haruka-chan?
Comment: 10,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.22,Alt,,0,0,0,***,Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.22,0:15:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm trying to say, Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.85,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.80,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying this restaurant should go, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, could you clarify what you mean by "go"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I said. It has to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.76,0:16:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.49,0:16:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.20,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Haruka!
Comment: 10,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{boom.jpeg}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.92,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been an explosion in town, \nten kilometres from here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The exact site is...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,***,Ayane?
Comment: 10,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,***,Ayane-chan?
Comment: 10,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.34,Alt,,0,0,0,***,Ayane?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.97,0:16:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The exact site is Shiba Seki Ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would anyone target that place?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What—No, {\i1}who{\i0} are they after?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.35,0:16:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Serika{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We can figure that out once we get there!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.61,0:16:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let her know.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry and help the boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.66,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just hold on, boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Owww...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's our Aru{**-chan}. Found her!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsuki, Kayoko…
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.08,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.01,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she even planted C4 \nin the ramen place...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.58,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, speaking of, what even was the plan with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I told you before.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Except this bit wasn't part of the plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what now?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, think about it. \nWasn't this exactly what you wanted?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.79,0:17:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted the restaurant gone, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.42,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Actually, I-I was the one who said that.{stuttering on "said" feels wrong imo -p}{### this better?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm completely fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.64,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, {*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.55,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I perhaps just made things worse?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.79,0:18:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be better to have \nmore bombs in more places, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point I should just die for my...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe later.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First things first, we should talk about...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.01,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Looking at this situation...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.88,0:18:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we the baddies? We are, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.18,0:18:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. Mission accomplished, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, wasn't the whole point to become a bad guy? {brings it a bit closer to the question --ik} {### og edit: "I mean, weren't you scared you were becoming a softie?" petz leaving it up to you}{i think i slightly prefer the og overall? works better with the follow-up lines. could go either way -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything those nice people did for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.09,0:18:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you were so terrified you'd grow a conscience, \nyou decided to blow up the entire place.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.48,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as cold-blooded and {**\n}ruthless as they come, Aru{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.82,0:18:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right! No morals! No mercy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay us the dime and we do the crime!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our motto!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.29,0:19:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well, if it isn't that \ncute little part-timer from Shiba Seki Ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.90,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You four... What do you think you're doing there?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows. Why don't you take a guess?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.50,0:19:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you the ones who destroyed Shiba Seki Ramen?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if we are?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.52,0:19:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll respond with appropriate force.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.82,0:19:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the girl, Aru{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it'd be so soon,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.65,0:19:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but we were going to have to \nsettle the score one of these days anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.25,0:19:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll make it right to you \nthis time, {*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}! I promise!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.96,0:19:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-Wh-Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.97,0:19:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I just come clean and give an honest apology?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.79,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I do, then our reputation as Problem Solver 68...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.48,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our {\i0}pride{\i1} as outlaws is toast!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she asked you a question!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there, say something!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who blew up Shiba Seki Ramen \nwere none other than us,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally getting the picture now? \nWe're bad to the bone!{rotating skull.gif -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.82,Alt,,0,0,0,,Aru{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss is secure!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.95,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Only minor injuries!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll escort him to the nearest shelter.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll rendezvous with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad he's okay, Serika{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.37,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Too damn far.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai},
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not calming down this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.42,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, then, have at you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dead! {don't drop the f bomb, don't drop the f bomb... --ik}{i mean, surely the show's at least PG13, we can drop one or two -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, what now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.63,0:21:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Them"?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But why now, of all times?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}! Please, wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}! {*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For the love of—Now what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.08,0:21:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we've been shelled by someone up ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.82,0:21:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Targets appear to be in disarray \nfollowing our mortar strike.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.45,0:21:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, how should we do this, Iori?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.46,0:21:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a couple unexpected guests with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.12,0:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, what's-their-face?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos, I think?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.56,0:21:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. The Abydos High School\n Foreclosure Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.21,0:22:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother asking? The answer's \nalways going to be the same, Chinatsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.02,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who interferes with our official duties...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.74,0:22:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{=5}is an enemy.

